          <ul class="catalog-notes">
              <li>Prerequisite: EPSC 203, EPSC 212, or equivalent</li>
              <li>This course, given in Sutton, has an additional fee of $531.44 to cover the costs of transportation, meals and accommodation as well as other field expenses. The fee is refundable during the period where a student can drop the course with full refund. The Department of Earth and Planetary Sciences subsidizes a portion of the cost for this activity.</li>
            </ul>
      </div>

