                <h4>Microbiology and Immunology</h4>

    
              <p>Prerequisites which cannot be counted toward the Minor concentration: <a href="/courses/biol-111">BIOL 111</a> and <a href="/courses/biol-112">BIOL 112</a>, <a href="/courses/chem-110">CHEM 110</a> and 120 or their equivalents.</p>
<p>Note: <a href="/courses/chem-212">CHEM 212</a> or its equivalent is prerequisite, or corequisite, to these courses.</p>
<p>Students select 15 credits from the following courses and their associated prerequisites:</p>
    
              <ul class="program-set">
                  <li class="program-course">
            <a href="/study/2014-2015/courses/biol-200" class="program-course-title">
              BIOL 200 Molecular Biology (3 credits)              <!---->            </a>
            <div class="program-course-description">
              <div class="program-course-description-inner">
                <div id="node-18752" class=" clearfix">
  
  
  
  <div class="meta">
    <p>Offered by: Biology (<a href="/study/2014-2015/node/615">Faculty of Science</a>)</p>
      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
